Sentencas: Distribution maps of carbon deposited on nickel particles were obtained by micro-Raman spectroscopy.
Titulo: Carbon deposition map for nickel particles onto oxide substrates analyzed by micro-Raman spectroscopy

Sentencas: Nickel film was prepared on the oxide substrates of yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) and gadolinia doped ceria (GDC).
Titulo: Carbon deposition map for nickel particles onto oxide substrates analyzed by micro-Raman spectroscopy

Sentencas: Carbon deposition was induced by annealing in dry methane for 10 min at both 863 and 933K. Morphology of nickel film was changed into particles with the size of several ten-nanometer to several micrometer at the edge of the nickel film after annealing.
Titulo: Carbon deposition map for nickel particles onto oxide substrates analyzed by micro-Raman spectroscopy

Sentencas: For the nickel/YSZ systems, carbon thoroughly deposited on all of sintered nickel particles but was not observed on YSZ surface.
Titulo: Carbon deposition map for nickel particles onto oxide substrates analyzed by micro-Raman spectroscopy

Sentencas: For the nickel/GDC systems, carbon was deposited only on the nickel particles with sub-micrometer size.
Titulo: Carbon deposition map for nickel particles onto oxide substrates analyzed by micro-Raman spectroscopy
